summary: This mod add a spell to the player that when casted will train any skill you desire.
descriptionHtml:
This mod add a spell to the player that when casted will train any skill you desire. When you cast it it will ask how fast you want to train. Some skills are different and how much is needed to increase your skill and will need to be faster when your at a higher skill level. And after you select which skill specialization and then select the skill and then train in that skill. After you finish training in a skill it will autosave incase you increase a skill too much after you can load the previous autosave. If you want the Skyrim Special Edition version go [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/1028/?]here[/url]. Also if you play Oblivion check out my [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/47248/?]Oblivion Level Booster.[/url]

Requirements
Skyrim

To install just download then extract folder and drag plugin, and bsa into your data folder.
author: LegoManIAm94
